data.thought: S17|H|S15|Multi-system Phenotype C2: 'Research Aggregator'. Notebook orchestrates: (1) Context7 queries for library docs (2) Firecrawl searches academic papers (3) GitHub API fetches related repos (4) Synthesizes into structured report. Thoughtbox: evaluates source credibility, identifies contradictions, generates citations, produces executive summary. Observable: source graph, credibility scores, synthesis reasoning. Use case: technical due diligence, literature review, competitive analysis.
